They then indicate a motion relative to the drawing position:
positive is down in vertical contexts,
right in horizontal ones.
.
.
.P
.B +
and
.B \-
are also treated differently by the following requests and escape
sequences:
.BR bp ,
.BR in ,
.BR ll ,
.BR pl ,
.BR pn ,
.BR po ,
.BR ps ,
.BR pvs ,
.BR rt ,
.BR ti ,
.BR \[rs]H ,
.BR \[rs]R ,
and
.BR \[rs]s .
